Joshuachem Pustok
Joshuachem Pustok tin bhagamnim vanttun ieta :

'''Poilo bhag :''' 

Bhasailolo Ganv jikhun ghetat   	Ovesvor 1 – 12

'''Dusro bhag  :'''  

Kullam modem des vantt’tat	Ovesvor 13- 21

a)	 Jordana udente vatten aslolo des	13/1-33

b)	Jordana ostomte vatten aslolo des 	14/1 – 19/51

c)	Asro gheupachim xaram		20/1-9

d)	Levitanchim xaram			21/1-45


'''Tisro bhag :''' 

Joshuachea jivitachi vat sompta	Ovesvor  22- 24
	
a)	 Udentichim kullam aplea desant portotat	   22/1-34

b)	Joshuacho nimanno nirop (farewell address)   23/1-16

c)	Shekem desant korar novsortat		   24/1-33


Judevanche porompore pormannem hem pustok Joshuan borounk na. Moizesachea mornna uprant Joshuachea fuddariponna khal Israelitamnim,  Kanaan desacher akromonn kelem tem hea pustokachi kheritai zaun asa.  Hea pustokant vornniloleo kaim mhotvacheo ghoddnneo he porim asat :

i)	Jordan nod utrop

ii)	Jeriko xar jikhun ghevop

iii)	Ai xar jikhun ghevop

iv)	Deva ani porje modem korar.


Hantli ek mhotvachi voll mhollear,  “Punn Sorvesporachi seva korunk tumi toiar nant zalear, konnachi kortoleat tem aizuch venchun kaddat…. Punn hanv ani mhojem kuttumb Sorvesporachi seva kortoleanv.” (24/15).

